

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include ./partials/head.ejs %>
<body>
  <% include /partials/header.ejs %>
  <div class="container landing-page-container">

    <div class="row">
      <div class="panning-banner">
        <div class="bg-banner" id="bg-keyframes"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="overlay">
        <div class="text" >
          <h2 class="shadow">Work smarter. Not harder.</h2>
          <p class="shadow">We know your busy life leaves you no time to manage all of the paperwork you collect on the road.
            After being gone all day no one wants to do more paper pushing when they get home. We get it.
            Mrkt Tracker is the easiest way to organize and maintain all of your professional contacts and notes in one place.
          </p>
          <% if(!user){%>
            <p class="btn-row">
              <a href="/login" class="btn btn-default raised btn-lg"><span class="fa fa-user fa-space-after"></span>Login</a>
              <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-default raised btn-lg"><span class="fa fa-sign-in fa-space-after"></span>Signup</a>
            </p>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container landing-description-container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="row-landing-content text">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h2>Have all your data in one place</h2>
            <p>Say goodbye to hunting through your address book, flipping through file folders,
              and searching through your old emails. Mrkt Tracker gives you one place to store all of the
              valuable information you need while on the go.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <img src="/images/devices.png">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>



      <div class="row">
        <div class="row-landing-content text">
          <div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6 col-md-6">
            <h2>Your stores at a glance</h2>
            <p>View all of your stores on one page. Mobile signal weak? No need to wait for
              a whole page to load. View summaries of each of your operators all in one place.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-pull-6 col-md-6">
            <img src="/images/iphone.png">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>



      <div class="row">
        <div class="row-landing-content text">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h2>Access from anywhere</h2>
            <p>Stuck at one of your locations, just waiting around? Mrkt Tracker goes with you, and can be accessed
              from any device. No more down-time, so when you get home your work is done.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <img src="/images/devices.png">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>



      <div class="row">
        <div class="row-landing-content text">
          <div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6 col-md-6">
            <h2>Keep your notes up to date</h2>
            <p>Things change on the fly. You need to be able to update your data just as quickly. With Mrkt Tracker,
              you can change your notes, locations, and operator statuses on the fly.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6 col-md-6">
            <img src="/images/iphone.png">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <% include /partials/footer.ejs %>
</body>
</html>
